Just recently, Cameronian singer cum actress, Ashley Stephanie got featured in a Nigerian movie, where she played Femi Jacobs side chick, since then, the internet has been agog wondering what’s going on between two talented actors. In a chat with Pearls News, Ashley said although she’s not in a relationship with Femi Jacobs but she’s a sucker for true love. Speaking on the celebrities that inspired her to effortlessly combine music and movies, Ashley Stephanie mentioned the likes of Beyonce and Kelly Roland. Wondering what the leggy artiste won’t do in the name of fashion? Hear her: “I can’t be caught wearing pantz or a G-string to a fashion show.” Source